'''Superfish'''（中國稱為'''快魚'''）是一間[[廣告軟體|廣告軟體]]公司，於2006年在[[以色列|以色列]]創立。總部位於[[加州|加州]]。

Superfish被不少人稱為[[惡意軟件|惡意軟件]]。<ref name=":0">{{cite web |url=https://www.us-cert.gov/ncas/alerts/TA15-051A |title=Alert: Lenovo "Superfish" Adware Vulnerable to HTTPS Spoofing |publisher=United States Computer Emergency Readiness Team |date=February 20, 2015 |accessdate=February 20, 2015 |archive-date=2017-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820211239/https://www.us-cert.gov/ncas/alerts/TA15-051A |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Lenovo's Superfish 'Malware'">{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/02/19/superfish-need-to-know/ |title=How Lenovo's Superfish 'Malware' Works And What You Can Do To Kill It |publisher=Forbes.com LLC |work=Forbes |date=February 19, 2015 |accessdate=February 20, 2015 |author=Fox-Brewster, Thomas |archive-date=2016-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207135447/http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/02/19/superfish-need-to-know/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2886827/bravo-windows-defender-update-fully-removes-lenovos-dangerous-superfish-malware.html |title=Bravo! Windows Defender update fully removes Lenovo's dangerous Superfish malware |publisher=PC World |date=February 20, 2015 |accessdate=February 20, 2015 |author=Chacos, Brad |archive-date=2016-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160212021549/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2886827/bravo-windows-defender-update-fully-removes-lenovos-dangerous-superfish-malware.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite web |url=http://thenextweb.com/insider/2015/02/19/lenovo-caught-installing-adware-new-computers/ |title=Lenovo caught installing adware on new computers |last=Williams |first=Owen |publisher=The Next Web |date=February 19, 2015 |accessdate=February 19, 2015 |archive-date=2016-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201170534/http://thenextweb.com/insider/2015/02/19/lenovo-caught-installing-adware-new-computers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/feb/19/lenovo-accused-compromising-user-security-installing-adware-pcs-superfish |first=Alex |last=Hern |title=Lenovo accused of compromising user security by installing adware on new PCs |publisher=The Guardian |date=February 19, 2015 |accessdate=February 19, 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117142152/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/feb/19/lenovo-accused-compromising-user-security-installing-adware-pcs-superfish |dead-url=no }}</ref>早於2010年，Superfish已經被用來捆綁其他軟件。<ref name=":0" />2014年9月，[[Lenovo|Lenovo]]開始在旗下筆記本電腦（不包括[[ThinkPad|ThinkPad]]和桌上型電腦）中預載Superfish。<ref>https://support.lenovo.com/product_security/superfish SUPERFISH軟體事件說明 - Lenovo Support</ref>被安裝的電子產品，不僅會持續彈出廣告、還有助駭客竊取用戶隱私資訊；該軟體還可自行簽發安全憑證，讓使用者「把有問題的網站誤認為安全」。

[[美聯社|美聯社]]2015年2月報導稱，Lenovo產品預載這款[[軟體|軟體]]是「安全大漏洞」，Lenovo 2月底回應宣告禁用該軟體，但在此前一度否認、強調快魚「不會保存/跟蹤用戶行為，也不記錄用戶信息。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2015/02/19/lenovo-stop-preloading-superfish/|title=Lenovo將不再為電腦預載Superfish軟體|accessdate=2015-03-07|publisher=ENGADGET|date=2015-02-20|archive-date=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224103445/http://chinese.engadget.com/2015/02/19/lenovo-stop-preloading-superfish/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2月末，Lenovo官方網站遭黑客攻擊。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/lenovo-website-taken-down-by-hackers/|title=Lenovo website hijacked just days after Superfish scandal|accessdate=2015-03-07|publisher=CNET|date=2015-02-25|archive-date=2015-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309033215/http://www.cnet.com/news/lenovo-website-taken-down-by-hackers/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 3月，Lenovo宣布將會向受影響用戶提供保安軟件。未來推出的新電腦上只會預載保安軟件和一些必要的[[驅動程式|驅動程式]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://unwire.hk/2015/03/03/lenovo-superfish-mcafee-livesafe/tech-secure/|title=送系統保安軟件Lenovo為Superfish事件補鑊|accessdate=2015-03-07|publisher=UNWIRE.HK|date=2015-03-03|archive-date=2015-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150305180523/http://unwire.hk/2015/03/03/lenovo-superfish-mcafee-livesafe/tech-secure/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Slate雜誌的一名編輯David Auerbach亦表示「安裝Superfish是一間科技公司史上最不負責任的過失」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Auerbach |first1=David |title=You Had One Job, Lenovo |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/bitwise/2015/02/lenovo_superfish_scandal_why_it_s_one_of_the_worst_consumer_computing_screw.html |accessdate=February 21, 2015 |work=Slate |date=February 20, 2015 |archive-date=2016-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201181756/http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/bitwise/2015/02/lenovo_superfish_scandal_why_it_s_one_of_the_worst_consumer_computing_screw.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

同年5月，Superfish易名JustVisual。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/security-scandal-tech-firm-changing-focus-31373750 |title=After Security Scandal, a Tech Firm Says It's Changing Focus |date=May 28, 2015 |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=May 31, 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529003146/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/security-scandal-tech-firm-changing-focus-31373750 |archivedate=2015-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

基於安全考量，資安專家建議購買聯想產品者「重新安裝Windows系統」<ref>{{cite news|author=大陸中心╱綜合外電報導|title=聯想預載軟體助駭客竊個資|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150221/36398885/聯想預載軟體助駭客竊個資|newspaper=臺灣[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]|date=201-02-21|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805130450/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150221/36398885/%E8%81%AF%E6%83%B3%E9%A0%90%E8%BC%89%E8%BB%9F%E9%AB%94%E5%8A%A9%E9%A7%AD%E5%AE%A2%E7%AB%8A%E5%80%8B%E8%B3%87|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年9月，联想与美国[[联邦贸易委员会|联邦贸易委员会]]（FTC）就此事引发的[[集体诉讼|集体诉讼]]达成和解，同意支付350万美元，并且在未来[[预装|预装]]软件前须征得消费者同意<ref>{{cite web|title=被指预装恶意广告软件 联想付350万美元与FTC和解|url=http://tech.qq.com/a/20170906/023320.htm|website=腾讯科技|accessdate=2017-09-06|archive-date=2017-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906091906/http://tech.qq.com/a/20170906/023320.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

